Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意不要掉队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:01:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是炸药
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这完全潮掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追兵马上就会追来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风雪过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始准备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利及其中央派来的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合计三人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看准空隙做掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由这里的成员执行作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对北方司令部的人也要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…迈尔斯少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做掉是指杀死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不赞成杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印他的链金术 叫他说出情报比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得那家伙会说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他活着太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 那家伙的部下呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人也许只是被迫变成合成兽而听命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但毕竟只是“也许”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因为可疑就杀死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷文中将那件事 也许还有别的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了布里克斯的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松警惕就会被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的天真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许哪天会夺去你与同伴的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地方不需要不谨慎的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利及另两名 就由我做掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说也是孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 在这个世界要贯穿不杀的理念太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我曾经也有那种想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了这个年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经历了几场战斗后就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起杀掉 不杀才更难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱力克兄弟选择了困难的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好事的家伙们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是也有点羡慕他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个LaSaYaNa是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够获得长寿的灵药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是指贤者之石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将所有的金属转变为金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将老人变成青年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个AUReRiAN是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金子的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽是有关长生不老与黄金的话题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡先生的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是受了清国链丹术的影响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在清国称不死之人为 真正的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既“真人”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是完全之人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从金也是完全的金属这层意思上讲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有把真人称为金人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全的人是金人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一种说法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把链金术传到清国的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拥有金发和金瞳的长生不老之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金发和金瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是爱德和阿尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 来这边 是出口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:05:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全穿越山脉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在向布里克斯进发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 你们跟着我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来雪很深呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 坐我背上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走在前面把雪踩实开出一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们跟在后面就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踩到深处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么被埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么阿尔会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过山脉 先绕过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过山脉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那暴风雪之中？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有迂回 笔直过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么做出这么乱来的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有紧急联络
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急联络？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央军进入了布里克斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮少将也被召去中央了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去要塞很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有藏到别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说别的地方 我们能去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离这里不远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个叫阿斯别克的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说同胞们住在那村子的贫民窟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊修瓦尔的贫民窟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎没有别的选择呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔突然不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会被金普利怀疑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥会随机应变的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三班 三名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四班 五名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么各自开始搜索所担当的地区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂 阿尔冯斯君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才应该说“好的”才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太好走动 爱德华君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 金普利在看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 金普利他们去搜查哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城镇中央有个很大的竖坑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要进那里来调查矿道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不信任北方的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只和中央都市派来的部下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙 察觉到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绕到前面去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在竖坑的附近找好狙击地点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找矿道的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有多个脚印就没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这个距离的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华君…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要调查矿道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给布里克斯兵不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面似乎非常复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你特意过来阻止我 也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜对了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想快点把斯卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说在争取配置狙击手的时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围有这么多杀气 当然会察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是白白活过了伊修瓦尔战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎在谈论什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能只瞄准金普利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪 要慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙 用雪做掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个大叔也是合成兽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 什么都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 对方也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半斤对八两…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖待着 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在视野不好的地区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法从我们的鼻子下逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈尔斯少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有合成兽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我习惯在视野不好的地方战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要进入雪烟里面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这样个子会变矮的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸药？不愧是矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别靠近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道这是什么吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 那种潮了的东西无法用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔们 知道炸药的原料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硝化甘油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硝化甘醇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木屑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有硝酸铵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 那个硝酸氨是什么组成的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是硝酸和氨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氨？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么味道？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是氨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻子太灵也很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们已经没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心人质 马上就这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想让你把知道的事情全都说出来罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 血气方刚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤刚好就和年轻人战斗 看来会费点力气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我也没空陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己拿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,链成阵也无法用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:14:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不杀的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很伟大的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 在战场上会变成空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那一瞬 你把我杀了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那份天真就是你的败因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉进竖坑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 金普利那家伙去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又被牵走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被什么牵走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎么了 铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂被牵走…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 以前有过这种事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能这样 让她哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 金普利那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 钢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有帮我把插在肚子上东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔掉的家伙… 会很困扰…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们把那根钢筋拔出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是敌人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有接到杀你的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 拔掉钢筋的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你立刻就会因大量失血而死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔掉的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大出血之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用链金术…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封住伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会用医疗系的链金术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要人体链成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概研究过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样子估计内脏完全乱七八糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不像金普利那样使用贤者之石的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为贤者之石的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然寿命也许会减少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是犹豫的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是自己的天真导致的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要自己补上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你没有犹豫的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拔了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己的生命想像成一种能量体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和贤者之石一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我现在是份量为灵魂的贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个使用生命的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别擅自把我杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有完全治好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把没事的组织连接起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时止血的急救措施
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 必须得去看医生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有那个闲工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去追金普利才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家很…危…险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 他是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种状态去战斗也没胜算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是金普利先生拿着的那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要叫他 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我们也卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 和那家伙说再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们算在这里死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这家伙怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总不能让他死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我们的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了外面要先去找医生才行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:23:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩断胶着的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:24:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开创道路所需要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.95,0:24:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外的想法和行动力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了隐藏之真实的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.42,0:24:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够抓住通向胜利的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.68,0:24:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那需要每天的积累
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.93,0:24:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.45,0:24:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第42话 反击的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.35,0:24:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 战争即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
